title: FRAM Extra Guard CA10755 Replacement Engine Air Filter for Select Lexus, Toyota, Jeep and Dodge Models, Provides Up to 12 Months or 12,000 Miles Filter Protection
description: FRAM Extra Guard Air Filters are your first line of defense preventing damaging road dust and dirt particles from entering your engine. Extra Guard Air Filters are engineered with an advanced filter media that lets through 2X less dirt than average leading standard retail brands AND protects your vehicle's engine up to 12 months or 12,000 miles. Replacing a dirty air filter with a new FRAM Extra Guard Air Filter can help increase horsepower, acceleration and overall engine performance. Get better protection with ease and install a new FRAM Extra Guard Air Filter today! Compatibility Models: 2011-2022 DODGE DURANGO V6 3.6L, 2011-2021 DODGE DURANGO V8 5.7L, 2018-2022 DODGE DURANGO V8 6.4L, 2011-2021 JEEP GRAND CHEROKEE V6 3.6L, 2011-2021 JEEP GRAND CHEROKEE V8 5.7L, 2012-2021 JEEP GRAND CHEROKEE V8 6.4L, 2022 JEEP GRAND CHEROKEE WK V6 3.6L, 2013-2018 LEXUS ES350 V6 3.5L, 2015-2017 LEXUS NX200T L4 2.0L, 2022 LEXUS NX250 L4 2.5L, 2018-2021 LEXUS NX300 L4 2.0L, 2010-2022 LEXUS RX350 V6 3.5L, 2018-2022 LEXUS RX350L V6 3.5L, 2013-2018 TOYOTA AVALON V6 3.5L, 2012-2017 TOYOTA CAMRY V6 3.5L, 2014-2019 TOYOTA HIGHLANDER L4 2.7L, 2014-2019 TOYOTA HIGHLANDER V6 3.5L, 2011-2013 TOYOTA SIENNA L4 2.7L, 2011-2020 TOYOTA SIENNA V6 3.5L
